commitResults.messageTitle: Rename chatbot as Saber and add Saber logo
Add Level 1 Requirements - Add Command enums - Add Greetings Message - Add Goodbye Message
Add Level 2 Requirements - Add listMessage - Add a String array with 100 elements to store tasks
commitResults.messageBody:
Variables totalTask and newTaskIndex were added in the main function
as the number of tasks and the index at which new task is added to
are linked to each runtime

- Add Command Class
- Add Task Class
- Add the ability to mark tasks as done
- Refactor main function:
        - To use Command Class
        - To use new functions in Saber Class
        - To use switch statement instead of if-else statement

commitResults.messageTitle: Add Level-4 Requirements - Add Todo, Event, and Deadline class - Rationale for hard coded + 4 in Command class   is because time is indicated by '/by' or '/at' which   are merely 4 chars. So + 4 is to remove the additional   '/by ' or '/at ' substring from the time variable
Add Level-5 Requirements - Add Custom Exception files - Handle Exceptions - Fix input parsing to be more strict
Add Level-6 Requirements - Add support for deleting tasks from the list - Change the way of storing tasks, from using array to arraylist
Remove trailing white spaces in print statements
Add A-TextUiTesting -Add Input and Expected output file to semi-automate the testing of Saber
